  textbox: {fileID: 0}
  sentences:
  - Before you start fighting you need to learn how to move and the resason why you
    are fighting.
  - The reason why you are fighting is to be crown king of the sticks by defeating
    the evil stick boss!
  - Use A and D on the keyboard to move back and forth. Press the space bar to jump.
  - Use H, J, K for simple attacks. Press L to block enemy attacks.
  - Use B and N to throw ninja stars.
  - If you feel ready or just skipped through instructions  click on fight to get
    started! You can't back out now!
  typingSpeed: 0.02
  ContinueButton: {fileID: 0}
  dialogPanel: {fileID: 0}
